1283.name: 316LMn
1283.Applications:
Particularly suited for corrosion conditions in urea synthesis plants for welding work on steel X 2 CrNiMo 18 12 and for over-lay claddings of Type 1.4455.. 
Well suited for joining and cladding applications with matching and similar austenitic CrNi(N) and CrNiMo(Mn,N) steels/cast steel grades.
